sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant MMSvc as ModelMesh Service<br/>(Kubernetes Service)
    participant RestProxy as rest-proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Marshaler as CustomJSONPb<br/>Marshaler/Unmarshaler
    participant GRPCClient as gRPC Client<br/>(grpc-gateway)
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh gRPC Server<br/>8033/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
        Client->>MMSvc: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>Optional TLS
        MMSvc->>RestProxy: Forward to pod port 8008
        RestProxy->>Marshaler: Decode JSON request body<br/>Handle nested tensor arrays<br/>Flatten multi-dim arrays<br/>Decode base64 BYTES tensors
        Marshaler->>GRPCClient: ModelInferRequest protobuf
        GRPCClient->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelInfer RPC<br/>localhost:8033<br/>Optional TLS
        ModelMesh-->>GRPCClient: ModelInferResponse protobuf
        GRPCClient-->>Marshaler: Marshal response
        Marshaler-->>RestProxy: JSON with RawOutputContents<br/>Binary-packed little-endian<br/>4-byte size delimiters
        RestProxy-->>MMSvc: HTTP 200 JSON response
        MMSvc-->>Client: Inference result
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request
        Client->>MMSvc: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>Optional TLS
        MMSvc->>RestProxy: Forward to pod port 8008
        RestProxy->>GRPCClient: ModelMetadata RPC call
        GRPCClient->>ModelMesh: gRPC ModelMetadata RPC<br/>localhost:8033<br/>Optional TLS
        ModelMesh-->>GRPCClient: ModelMetadataResponse
        GRPCClient-->>RestProxy: Marshal to JSON
        RestProxy-->>MMSvc: HTTP 200 JSON response
        MMSvc-->>Client: Model metadata
    end
